headline: Lennox Launches Gas Furnace Featuring Integrated Refrigerant Detection System
summary: Lennox Residential HVAC, a leader in energy-efficient home comfort solutions, announced today the release of the Dave Lennox Signature® SLP99VK Gas Furnace, designed to deliver high-efficiency heating with built-in refrigerant detection capability.
